description:
Ben Elton's deliberately short-lived comedy series starring Jennifer Saunders, Adrian Edmondson, Jennifer Saunders, Jennifer Saunders, Jennifer Saunders and heaps of other people who often appear in things with Ben Elton, Adrian Edmondson &amp; Jennifer Saunders. Sadly there's only one series. This is due to the fact that Ben Elton only ever intended to write one series. Producer Paul Jackson kept a slot in BBC's schedule for a 2nd series... knowing full well that Ben never intended on writing a 2nd series. Paul did this so that he could take a risk on a new series that only had a slim chance of succeeding. That show ended up being none other than RED DWARF! And you can quote me! :p

